              </a>
              <a href="/guides/cash-flow-basics" class="p-4 border border-[var(--color-border)] rounded-lg hover:border-emerald-500/50 transition-colors">
                <div class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-foreground)]">Cash Flow Basics</div>
